{#-
  Chatbot — conversational UI panel (Ring 3 S3.3c — FINAL Ring 3 pattern, 54e).

  Pure composition (per OQ-NEW Chatbot scope sealed pure composition NO lib —
  preserves Path Z signal NO 10e cascade) :
    - Drawer Ring 2 (edge=end default ; inline-end anchor for desktop /
      bottom anchor on mobile via consumer responsive class)
    - Input Ring 1 (text input for user message)
    - Item Ring 1 (as='div' for message bubbles, with data-role variants)

  Controller : chatbot (19th Ring 3, thin) — message append + auto-scroll
  on new message + send action dispatch + typing indicator toggle. Pure
  composition of Drawer/Input/Item ; consumer wires actual streaming /
  markdown rendering server-side or via custom event handler on
  chatbot:send.

  13th cross-controller compose instance : data-controller="drawer chatbot".

  Doctrine notes :
  - No markdown rendering at kit level (consumer ships plain text or
    pre-rendered HTML safely escaped). marked / similar lazy adapter
    deferred to Ring 4+ trigger per ADR-0033 §"Trade-offs deferred to
    Ring 4+" if real consumer demand surfaces.
  - aria-live="polite" on message list (per 13-accessibility-baseline §9
    screen-reader announcements for transient updates).
  - Typing indicator is decorative ; the actual bot response is announced
    via the new message landing in the aria-live region.

  Parameters:
    htmlId             (string, optional)
    title              (string, optional) — drawer title
    edge               (string, optional, default 'end') — drawer anchor
    placeholder        (string, optional)
    sendLabel          (string, optional) — send button aria label
    closeAriaLabel     (string, optional)
    greeting           (string, optional) — pre-seeded bot message displayed on open
    open               (bool,   optional, default false)
-#}

{%- set htmlId          = htmlId          | default('cremona-chatbot-' ~ random()) -%}
{%- set title           = title           | default('theme.chatbot.title'|trans) -%}
{%- set edge            = edge            | default('end') -%}
{%- set placeholder     = placeholder     | default('theme.chatbot.placeholder'|trans) -%}
{%- set sendLabel       = sendLabel       | default('theme.chatbot.aria.send'|trans) -%}
{%- set closeAriaLabel  = closeAriaLabel  | default('theme.chatbot.aria.close'|trans) -%}
{%- set greeting        = greeting        | default('theme.chatbot.greeting'|trans) -%}
{%- set open            = open            ?? false -%}

{%- set _cbId = htmlId -%}

{% embed '@cremona/components/drawer/drawer.html.twig' with {
  wrapId: _cbId,
  htmlId: _cbId ~ '-dialog',
  edge: edge,
  open: open,
  className: 'cremona-chatbot',
  drawerClassName: 'cremona-chatbot__dialog',
  headerClass: 'cremona-chatbot__header',
  bodyClass: 'cremona-chatbot__body',
  footerClass: 'cremona-chatbot__footer',
  controllerExtras: 'chatbot',
  closeAriaLabel: closeAriaLabel,
} %}
  {% block title %}{{ title }}{% endblock %}

  {% block body %}
    <ol class="cremona-chatbot__messages"
        data-chatbot-target="messages"
        aria-live="polite"
        aria-atomic="false">
      {%- if greeting -%}
        <li class="cremona-chatbot__message" data-role="bot">
          {% include '@cremona/components/item/item.html.twig' with {
            as: 'div',
            label: greeting,
            attrs: { 'data-chatbot-target': 'messageTemplate' },
          } only %}
        </li>
      {%- endif -%}
    </ol>

    <div class="cremona-chatbot__typing"
         data-chatbot-target="typing"
         data-active="false"
         aria-hidden="true">
      <span class="cremona-chatbot__typing-text">{{ 'theme.chatbot.typing'|trans }}</span>
      <span class="cremona-chatbot__typing-dots" aria-hidden="true">
        <span></span><span></span><span></span>
      </span>
    </div>
  {% endblock %}

  {% block footer %}
    <form class="cremona-chatbot__form"
          data-action="submit->chatbot#send"
          novalidate>
      {% include '@cremona/components/label/label.html.twig' with {
        htmlFor: _cbId ~ '__input',
        content: 'theme.chatbot.input.label'|trans,
        className: 'sr-only',
      } only %}
      {% include '@cremona/components/input/input.html.twig' with {
        type: 'text',
        htmlId: _cbId ~ '__input',
        name: 'message',
        placeholder: placeholder,
        autocomplete: 'off',
        required: true,
        className: 'cremona-chatbot__input',
        attrs: { 'data-chatbot-target': 'input' },
      } only %}
      {% include '@cremona/components/button/button.html.twig' with {
        type: 'submit',
        variant: 'primary',
        iconLeading: 'arrow-right',
        ariaLabel: sendLabel,
        className: 'cremona-chatbot__send',
      } only %}
    </form>
  {% endblock %}
{% endembed %}
